This project is ORCHESTRATED: production code on `main` is built only from PR merges, never
direct commits. The presence of this file activates the global main-protection hook
(~/.claude/hooks/main-protection.sh), which denies non-`.md` commits while on the default branch.
Brain docs (`*.md`) are exempt — the planning session commits those to main directly.

Remove this file to opt out of merge-only main.
